      <div class='info-container instructions'>
        <h2 class='info-container__title'>Creating a Wifi Hotspot Problem</h2>
        <div class='btn-container'>
          <button class='btn--small' type="button" name="prev">Previous</button>
          <button class='btn--small' type="button" name="next">Next</button>
        </div>
        <div class='info-container__details instructions'>
          <ul class='info-container__list'>
            <li>It is relatively easy to create one of these problems.</li>
            <li>It may be very difficult for someone else to solve your problem!</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 class='to-do'>Follow the instructions to create your own Wifi Hotspot Problem!</h3>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!--
      {{> key}}
      -->
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

